Define "the Model": The collection of files and builds representing the
the Portal Modular Testing Chamber system by Andrey Risukhin, and 
derivatives of those files and builds. 

The following restrictions ("the Restrictions") are imposed to maintain
compliance with Lego Ideas guidelines (https://ideas.lego.com/guidelines)
while allowing for the Lego fan community to collaboratively build on the
Model, improving it for anyone to create. 

Define "Restriction 1": The original creator, Andrey Risukhin, maintains 
the exclusive right to submit a subset of the Model to LEGO Ideas. 

Define "Restriction 2": Persons obtaining a copy of this software and 
associated documentation files ("the Software") are prohibited from selling 
building instructions, custom kits, or anything related to the Portal Modular
Testing Chamber system, and from otherwise causing this project to be 
invalid as a future Lego Ideas submission. 

